(2, 1, '平台服务协议', '<p style="text-align:center"></p><p style="text-indent:28px"><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:宋体">本《</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:宋体">一点椿</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:宋体">平台用户服务合作协议》（以下简称</span>“本协议”）由用户与广东保椿信息科技</span><span style=";font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:宋体">有限公司（</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:宋体">以下简称</span></span><span style=";font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px">“</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:宋体">一点椿</span></span><span style=";font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px">”<span style="font-family:宋体">或</span><span style="font-family:Calibri">“</span><span style="font-family:宋体">我们</span><span style="font-family:Calibri">”</span><span style="font-family:宋体">）</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:宋体">签订，适用于用户访问</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:宋体">一点椿</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:宋体">平台（包括但不限于其</span>APP<span style="font-family:宋体">、小程序、网站、后台管理程序及系统、数据库等，合称“</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:宋体">一点椿</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:宋体">平台</span>”），以及用户通过</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:宋体">一点椿</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:宋体">平台获得相关网络信息、建议和技术服务等全部相关事宜。</span></span></p><p style="text-indent:28px"><span style=";font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:宋体">在此特别提醒用户，在</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:宋体">使用</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:宋体">一点椿</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:宋体">平台各项服务之</span></span><span style=";font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:宋体">前，请用户</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:宋体">务必</span></span><span style=";font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:宋体">仔细阅读本协议</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:宋体">，</span></span><span style=";font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:宋体">用户注册、登录、下载、安装、使用</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:宋体">一点椿</span></span><span style=";font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:宋体">平台及相关服务等行为将被视为对本协议全部内容</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:宋体">法律概念以及法律后果</span></span><span style=";font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:宋体">的</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:宋体">认可和完全接受</span></span><span style=";font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:宋体">。</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:宋体">如对本声明内容有任何疑问，用户可及时与我们联系。</span></span><span style=";font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:宋体">我们有权根据</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:宋体">一点椿</span></span><span style=";font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:宋体">平台及其服务的更新而修改本协议各条款，用户可通过可在</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:宋体">一点椿</span></span><span style=";font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:宋体">平台查阅最新版本协议条款。在我们修改本协议条款后，如用户不接受修改后的条款，请停止使用</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:宋体">一点椿</span></span><span style=";font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:宋体">平台及其服务，用户继续登录、下载、安装、使用</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:宋体">一点椿</span></span><span style=";font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:宋体">平台及相关服务等行为视为对修改后的协议的认同及接受，并同意接受修改后的协议各条款的约束。</span></span></p><p><span style=";font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="text-indent:28px"><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px"><span style="font-family:宋体">一</span></span></strong><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px"><span style="font-family:宋体">、一点椿</span></span></strong><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px"><span style="font-family:宋体">帐户</span></span></strong></p><p><span style=";font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px">&nbsp;</span></p><p><span style=";font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;1.1<span style="font-family:宋体">为了使用我们提供的服务，用户需要在使用前注册一个</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:宋体">一点椿</span></span><span style=";font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:宋体">帐户，帐户名请用用户所提供的常用手机号码注册。通过</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:宋体">一点椿</span></span><span style=";font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:宋体">平台下发的手机验证码完成</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:宋体">一点椿</span></span><span style=";font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:宋体">帐户验证后，该帐户即可以使用。用户在</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:宋体">一点椿</span></span><span style=";font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:宋体">平台下单前需选择、登记服务对象的信息（以下简称</span>“<span style="font-family:宋体">看护对象</span><span style="font-family:Calibri">”</span><span style="font-family:宋体">）。</span></span></p><p><span style=";font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px">&nbsp;</span></p><p><span style=";font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;1.2<span style="font-family:宋体">鉴于</span><span style="font-family:Calibri">“</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:宋体">一点椿</span></span><span style=";font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:宋体">帐号</span>”<span style="font-family:宋体">的绑定注册方式，用户同意本公司在用户注册时将使用用户提供的手机号码及</span><span style="font-family:Calibri">/</span><span style="font-family:宋体">或自动提取用户的手机号码及自动提取用户的手机设备识别码等信息用于注册。</span></span></p><p><span style=";font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px">&nbsp;</span></p><p><span style=";font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;1.3<span style="font-family:宋体">用户有义务在注册时提供自己及看护对象的真实资料，并保证诸如电子邮件地址、联系电话、联系地址等内容的有效性和安全性，保证我们、</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:宋体">一点椿</span></span><span style=";font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:宋体">平台及其用户可以通过上述联系方式与用户或看护对象联系。同时，用户也有义务在相关资料实际变更时及时更新有关注册资料。用户保证不以他人信息资料在</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:宋体">一点椿</span></span><span style=";font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:宋体">平台进行注册。</span></span></p><p><span style=";font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px">&nbsp;</span></p><p><span style=";font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;1.4<span style="font-family:宋体">用户可以在</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:宋体">一点椿</span></span><span style=";font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:宋体">帐户中查询到用户的订单记录，包括为用户提供服务的</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:宋体">家护师</span></span><span style=";font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:宋体">信息及所提供服务的具体地点记录等。用户应负责维护用户的帐户的保密性及安全性，保证不以任何形式擅自转让或授权他人使用用户的</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:宋体">一点椿</span></span><span style=";font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:宋体">帐号，并且，用户同意对在用户的帐户和密码</span>/<span style="font-family:宋体">验证码下发生的所有活动承担责任。如果用户未满</span><span style="font-family:Calibri">18</span><span style="font-family:宋体">周岁，用户只能在父母或监护人的参与下使用服务。我们保留自行决定终止提供服务、关闭帐户、删除 或编辑内容或取消订单的权利。</span></span></p><p><span style=";font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px">&nbsp;</span></p><p><span style=";font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;1.5<span style="font-family:宋体">如发生利用计算机程序等其他技术手段进行恶意注册、邀请、参与的情形，我们有权在不事先通知用户的情况下单方面中断或终止向用户提供服务而无需通知用户。</span></span></p><p><span style=";font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="text-indent:28px"><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px"><span style="font-family:宋体">二</span></span></strong><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px"><span style="font-family:宋体">、一点椿</span></span></strong><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px"><span style="font-family:宋体">服务</span></span></strong></p><p><span style=";font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px">&nbsp;</span></p><p><span style=";font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="font-family:宋体">用户应了解并知悉，</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:宋体">一点椿</span></span><span style=";font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:宋体">可供用户选择并预约的服务品类及专题版块包括但不限于：老人照护、康复护理服务</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:宋体">信息</span></span><span style=";font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:宋体">，具体以用户用户登陆服务选择页面时最新展示列出的服务品类</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:宋体">信息</span></span><span style=";font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:宋体">为准。对于非自营</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:宋体">家护师</span></span><