font-family:宋体;font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:宋体">一点椿</span></span><span style=";font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:宋体">将通过电子邮件、短信、在本网站上发布通知或其它服务与用户进行联系。用户同意我们用这些方式提供给用户的所有协议、通知、披露和其他信息是符合相关的法律法规要求的。如果我们以该等形式向用户发出信息或者在本网站上发出相关通知，将视为用户已收到所有协议、声明、披露和其它信息。</span></span></p><p><span style=";font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px">&nbsp;</span></p><p><span style=";font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;1</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px">3</span><span style=";font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px">.2</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:宋体">一点椿</span></span><span style=";font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:宋体">郑重提醒用户注意本协议中有限责任等条款，请用户仔细阅读，自主考虑风险。未成年人应在法定代理人</span>/<span style="font-family:宋体">监护人的陪同下阅读本协议。</span></span></p><p><span style=";font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px">&nbsp;</span></p><p><span style=";font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;1</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px">3</span><span style=";font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px">.3</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:宋体">一点椿</span></span><span style=";font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:宋体">保留对本协议的解释权与修改权。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>', '', '2019-09-21 14:49:00', 0);
